WEBVTT

00:14.467 --> 00:15.717
<b>You can have this.{ep06@10:51}</b>

00:19.557 --> 00:21.807
<b>They erode the bones.{ep06@10:54}</b>

00:21.807 --> 00:26.257
<b>Looks like we're going to be together
 for quite a while, so it'd be nice if you smoked too.{ep06@10:57}</b>

00:31.857 --> 00:33.517
<b>Fine, I'll smoke <i>one</i>.{ep06@11:11}</b>

00:34.057 --> 00:37.377
<b>And this will be the only one I smoke with you.{ep06@11:13}</b>

00:37.377 --> 00:39.867
<b>Yay! Let me light it up for you.</b>

00:40.927 --> 00:44.167
<b>Pushing a minor to smoke. You're the worst.</b>

00:44.167 --> 00:46.047
<b>What? You're underage?!</b>

00:46.047 --> 00:47.277
<b>Yes.</b>

00:47.277 --> 00:50.627
<b>Then of course you shouldn't be smoking.</b>

00:56.037 --> 00:56.987
<b>Give it back.</b>

01:00.007 --> 01:03.447
<b>I'll keep this one for you.</b>

01:06.007 --> 01:10.767
<b>When you grow up and need
 something to lean on, I'll give it to you again.</b>

02:25.697 --> 02:29.637
<b><i>The Ghost Devil has no eyes, so it can only sense fear.</i></b>

02:30.597 --> 02:32.597
<b><i>That's what Himeno told me.</i></b>

02:50.987 --> 02:51.907
<b><i>Himeno,</i></b>

02:54.537 --> 02:56.137
<b><i>I'll be joining you soon.</i></b>

03:40.127 --> 03:40.747
<b>Snake!</b>

03:40.747 --> 03:41.247
<b>Don't kill her.</b>

04:00.127 --> 04:03.517
<b>Kobeni, why did you stay in the Bureau?</b>

04:08.417 --> 04:10.937
<b>Because our bonuses are coming up.</b>

04:28.417 --> 04:30.417
<b>Ew!</b>

04:31.647 --> 04:33.797
<b>What?! It's just meat.</b>

04:34.247 --> 04:36.177
<b>Pig, cow, or human, it's all the same.</b>

04:36.557 --> 04:38.227
<b>It's completely different.</b>

04:39.867 --> 04:43.017
<b>Our job is to catch the samurai-sword dude.</b>

04:43.407 --> 04:45.387
<b>Don't go eating him when we get him!</b>

04:47.077 --> 04:47.647
<b>Why, you!</b>

04:58.257 --> 05:00.177
<b>They haven't noticed us.</b>

05:00.177 --> 05:02.077
<b>Keep it quiet.</b>

05:04.617 --> 05:06.497
<b>My name is Power!{lmao}</b>

05:06.497 --> 05:07.377
<b>Huh?!</b>

05:07.377 --> 05:08.827
<b>I can beat these lot.</b>

05:08.827 --> 05:10.207
<b>Fight me!</b>

05:12.407 --> 05:14.337
<b>Denji, follow me!</b>

05:14.957 --> 05:16.547
<b>Watch my back!</b>

05:21.547 --> 05:22.597
<b>How's this?!</b>

05:22.597 --> 05:23.557
<b>What say you?!</b>

05:23.937 --> 05:25.057
<b>I'm not running away!</b>

05:25.357 --> 05:27.487
<b>Is this not a noble and beautiful fight?!</b>

05:30.407 --> 05:31.947
<b>That is a powerful one.</b>

05:31.947 --> 05:33.717
<b>Look well, Denji!</b>

05:33.717 --> 05:35.187
<b>And tell everyone!</b>

05:35.587 --> 05:38.387
<b>How Power is the strongest of all!</b>

06:05.837 --> 06:07.517
<b>Well, if it isn't Mister Sideburns!</b>

06:07.987 --> 06:09.437
<b>Whoa, whoa, whoa!</b>

06:09.437 --> 06:11.277
<b>How about we talk a bit first?</b>

06:11.277 --> 06:12.447
<b>What?!</b>

06:15.657 --> 06:19.827
<b>We're thinking of maybe surrendering depending on how you would treat us.</b>

06:20.477 --> 06:23.527
<b>We just want to resolve this anger within us.</b>

06:28.117 --> 06:32.987
<b>Denji, you killed these guys' comrades and my grandpa.</b>

06:33.437 --> 06:35.667
<b>We'd like you to make amends for that.</b>

06:35.987 --> 06:40.297
<b>I only killed them after
 they'd already turned into zombies.</b>

06:40.297 --> 06:41.717
<b>Don't lie to us!</b>

06:41.717 --> 06:44.847
<b>Uneducated fools like you lie without even thinking!</b>

06:46.597 --> 06:48.057
<b>But anyway,</b>

06:48.057 --> 06:51.137
<b>even if what you're saying is true,</b>

06:51.137 --> 06:52.977
<b>zombies used to be humans.</b>

06:53.417 --> 06:56.607
<b>Don't you feel anything about killing them?</b>

06:57.057 --> 06:58.107
<b>Nothing at all.</b>

07:00.767 --> 07:03.497
<b>Sawatari did things to me too.</b>

07:03.497 --> 07:07.367
<b>My heart was replaced with the Sword Devil.</b>

07:07.877 --> 07:10.037
<b>But even like this,</b>

07:10.037 --> 07:13.837
<b>I couldn't sleep after I killed a zombie by mistake.</b>

07:14.937 --> 07:18.997
<b>But you, you seem to have lost all of your humanity.</b>

07:19.417 --> 07:22.257
<b>If you have a modicum of human conscience left,</b>

07:22.917 --> 07:25.767
<b>you should just let us kill you.</b>

07:31.857 --> 07:32.897
<b>Nah.</b>

07:34.947 --> 07:36.317
<b>I see.</b>

07:37.017 --> 07:38.857
<b>Then I'll just have to cut you down!</b>

07:39.317 --> 07:41.367
<b>Let's see you try, dumbass!</b>

07:49.837 --> 07:50.747
<b>What?!</b>

07:50.737 --> 07:54.367
<b>What's the matter, weren't you gonna cut me or something?</b>

08:01.877 --> 08:02.757
<b>Drop dead!</b>

08:07.697 --> 08:09.017
<b>Shit.</b>

08:48.207 --> 08:50.637
<b>You're doing a bit better than last time.</b>

08:50.997 --> 08:54.637
<b>What are you fighting for, Denji?</b>

08:55.587 --> 08:58.257
<b>To protect my new way of life.</b>
